title: Tammy Hembrow displays her impossibly tiny waist in a pink PVC bikini
text:
She's the busty Gold Coast beauty who has been labelled 'Australia's Kim Kardashian'.

And Tammy Hembrow, 25, proved she won't be giving up her title any time soon as she shared a snap of herself in a tiny pink bikini on Instagram this Tuesday.

The blonde bombshell, who boasts an impressive 9.9 million Instagram followers, showcased her impossibly tiny waist and prodigious derrière as she posed by her backyard pool.

Kim Kardashian, eat your heart out! Tammy Hembrow, 25, displayed her impossibly tiny waist and eye-popping derrière as he posed by the pool in a pink PVC bikini on Tuesday

Running one hand through her slicked-back locks, the mother-of-two stared intensely into the distance as she gently leaned on a glass bannister.

'How bomb is @ohpolly new electrical storm collection,' Tammy wrote in the caption, promoting the designer of her PVC bikini.

Also on display was Tammy's ever-growing collection of tattoos, including a seahorse inked on her upper thigh and a large floral design on her back.

She's got competition! The busty Gold Coast beauty has been labelled 'Australia's Kim Kardashian' (pictured)

'Spot the new tatt': It comes after the glamazon debuted her newest tattoo on Instagram on Saturday, uploading an Instagram Story video of herself brandishing a large black star inked behind her right ear

Tatt's a lot of ink! Tammy's extensive collection of ink includes a seahorse on her upper thigh and a butterfly on her forearm

The glamazon debuted her newest tattoo on Instagram on Saturday, uploading an Instagram Story video of herself brandishing a large black star inked behind her right ear.

'Spot the new tatt,' teased Tammy as she pouted towards the camera in the front seat of her car.

She then turned her head slightly and pulled back her ponytail to debut the bold black design.

Strength: In January, Tammy revealed that she'd had a pair of angel wings tattooed on her back to represent all the 'hard times' she'd been through in recent years

It's unclear whether the design holds any particular symbolic meaning for the social media sensation.

In January, Tammy revealed that she'd had a pair of angel wings tattooed on her back to represent all the 'hard times' she'd been through in recent years.

'It was a lot to go through and this was my symbol for strength... and to represent my faith,' she said, referencing her split from Reece Hawkins in 2018.
description: She's the busty Gold Coast beauty who has been labelled 'Australia's Kim Kardashian'.
authors: Monique Friedlander For Daily Mail Australia
